The new short story 'The Voice of Death' can now be read on Inkitt, Wattpad or here on the site.

<h3>summary:</h3>
<hr class="solid"/>
Marius, a speaker, possesses the ability to bind any living creature to his command. Only those versed in the way of the iron heart such as the emperor and his royal Mastas, are able to withstand their compelling words. Born into servitude, Marius must fight the enemies of the empire under the watchful eyes of the Mastas. As he once again heeds the command of the Emperor in the defense of the city of Saint Mera.
